---
title: Double Teriyaki Beef & Broccoli Stir-Fry with Ginger Rice
description: It doesn’t get much more simple and delicious than this beef and broccoli stir-fry. Our teriyaki sauce is the perfect addition, bringing tonnes of flavour in just one ingredient. Don’t forget the fragrant rice - the subtle heat of our punchy
ginger paste adds an aromatic twist. No need to wait, dig in while it’s hot!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6792fedb5ca0a783e56238db-30c3a782-f7e0cffc.jpeg
